<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_b2793ce3-60fd-4d5e-b4ab-8e1a63b7d42f" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><sptc>I4D5</sptc><title id="_edefb6cf-3e9e-4735-833a-83750a56f93d">Provision for escape</title><subclause id="_58179f2f-b175-45de-8746-59665469b9bf" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_1f54bc48-cae7-4bba-88e8-eb6f51da369c">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>In addition to any horizontal exit, not less than 2 exits must be provided from—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_9cdc9069-8765-437f-9456-9bf248d45c28">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2474_25.0.0.xml#_638ea3e1-f483-40cc-9e79-5291637c5f3e" id="_8bce70ad-87ec-43a5-81fb-c118a1ea4b98" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storage shed</xref> in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_f6f6931f-f2d3-4fc8-b171-8530fd73fda8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref> if the distance of travel to an exit is more than 150 m; and</li><li id="_1f8099f6-a04c-4d99-bc7a-0adef04f33f5">the gallery level in a cell type silo in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_35f17ec2-91e9-448f-9fd4-f587022be59b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_2a216b2e-491a-4f78-8e36-84ad6581c783" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_701f2e0d-4270-42bf-ab58-d55dea868692">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A stairway or ramp serving as a required exit from a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_19e90a5b-d436-430c-9c6a-03945a387640" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref> is not required to be fire-isolated where there are no window or door openings within 3 m of the stairway, ramp or ladder.</p></subclause><subclause id="_ef9b475a-8c5c-4e2b-8138-8e907c0084bf" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_34bdda0b-cc4f-40ba-a560-edaed9f21a8e">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>Where required exits are spaced not more than 100 m apart in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_95335d21-8e50-4321-8fa7-40ce5bd09790" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref>, the travel distance to an exit in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2468_0.7.0.xml#_77fc5383-ae28-4bfd-ad12-0d5735cf1366" id="_805c5181-956e-430a-b75f-e49ccbfe45b9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">cell type silo</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2474_25.0.0.xml#_638ea3e1-f483-40cc-9e79-5291637c5f3e" id="_ae56de71-e524-49c1-91ff-0db9f3e45cda" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storage shed</xref> is not limited to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1491_1.6.0.xml#_6def630a-bd18-41d6-8931-ca82da5ed6f4" id="_c00f93d1-ac17-4c65-9496-c4b2f300b723" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">D2D5(3)</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_c52f0339-2614-4dd3-92fe-59a96e3cb740" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8236f33e-4eba-48a4-8ae8-59b1f837292b">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>In a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_b2909e60-4edc-4262-848a-66c57f3e7e00" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref>, the distance from any point on the floor to a point of egress to a road or open space by way of a non-fire-isolated stairway, non-fire-isolated ramp or ladder is not limited.</p></subclause><subclause id="_bd41a193-9d72-453f-848b-1a63bb73d5c5" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_15ad2fae-5941-4b60-bf95-56e1cf588ee6">SubClause</title><num>5</num><p>A stair or ladder complying with AS 1657 may be used in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2466_1.0.0.xml#_0ea6e30e-b7ce-4b3d-ab37-7888621a4eac" id="_e1358193-eac5-43a1-8efe-c3e8a53dd6ec" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">bulk grain storage facility</xref> as an alternative means of egress from a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/2468_0.7.0.xml#_77fc5383-ae28-4bfd-ad12-0d5735cf1366" id="_7cff0996-b61b-49e0-9636-ac9db9a33aaf" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">cell type silo</xref>.</p></subclause></clause>